OL,6,FAlong the way they are faced with
OL,7,Fchallenges such as river crossings,
OL,8,Fmass casualty scenarios and minefield
OL,9,Fclearances in an event designed to
OL,10,Ftest their endurance, skills and
OL,11,Fleadership abilities.
OL,13,FIn the run-up to the event, the former
OL,14,Fregular army soldier, who is now a
OL,15,Freservist with 7 Scots, led his team
OL,16,Fthrough a rigorous training regime
OL,17,Ffocusing on navigation exercises and
OL,18,Fessential military drills.
