OL,3,CReservist, 55, becomes oldest person
OL,4,Cto complete Nato's toughest challenge
OL,6,FCorporal Declan Hood, 26, also serves
OL,7,Fwith the Royal Regiment of Scotland.
OL,9,FMajor Hood added: "I knew he didn't
OL,10,Fhave a training at the time, so I got
OL,11,Fin touch and arranged for him to be
OL,12,Freleased. He completed his medical,
OL,13,Fand we got him on board."
OL,15,FThe 55-year-old reflected that having
OL,16,Fhis son alongside him on the course
OL,17,F"made a big difference".
