OL,3,CReservist, 55, becomes oldest person
OL,4,Cto complete Nato's toughest challenge
OL,6,F"It was a real once-in-a-lifetime
OL,7,Fexperience to share with Declan. At
OL,8,Fone point, he really kept me going,"
OL,9,Fhe said.
OL,11,F"The toughest moment came after the
OL,12,Friver crossing ` running on just an
OL,13,Fhour of sleep, soaked through in only
OL,14,Fwaterproofs, and freezing ` it was
OL,15,Fhard to stay motivated.
OL,17,F"I fell into a drainage ditch but
OL,18,FDeclan was there to pull me out.
OL,19,FHaving him there, both for support and
OL,20,Fto help physically, made a big
OL,21,Fdifference."
