OL,3,CReservist, 55, becomes oldest person
OL,4,Cto complete Nato's toughest challenge
OL,6,FMajor Hood, who joined the army in
OL,7,F1985, had already completed the
OL,8,Fchallenge once before in 1992, when he
OL,9,Fwas in his 20s.
OL,11,FHowever he said this time round it was
OL,12,Feven more rewarding due to the
OL,13,Fteamwork and camaraderie in the 7
OL,14,FScots team.
OL,16,F"I originally had no intention of
OL,17,Fdoing it, but after training with the
OL,18,Fteam and seeing their dedication and
OL,19,Fhard work, I felt I had to take part,"
OL,20,Fhe said.
