OL,3,CReservist, 55, becomes oldest person
OL,4,Cto complete Nato's toughest challenge
OL,6,F"I was in my 20s back in 1992, and
OL,7,Fwhile I may not have the same physical
OL,8,Fstamina, my mentality has certainly
OL,9,Fstrengthened from years of experience
OL,10,Fin service."
OL,12,F"It was a true team effort. I couldn't
OL,13,Fhave done it without the rest of the
OL,14,Ftroops.
OL,16,F"They were an inspiration, and the way
OL,17,Fthey represented 7 Scots and the Army
OL,18,FReserve is something to be truly proud
OL,19,Fof."
